{"article_id":"Zp6jGneN4Rrm3Wwi","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"US President Donald Trump insists","depth":8},{"id":1,"text":"the US will still build a wall along its border with Mexico ,","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"despite ending the longest-ever US government shutdown","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"without securing funds for the project .","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"On Twitter , Mr Trump said","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"the deal","depth":10},{"id":6,"text":"to temporarily reopen government","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"was `` in no way a concession '' on the wall .","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"The bipartisan agreement","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"announced on Friday","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"covers just three weeks .","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"Mr Trump indicated","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"he might trigger another shutdown","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"or declare a national emergency","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"if his demands are not met .","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"The Republican president has vowed to reject any budget","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"unless Congress includes $ 5.7bn","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"( £4.3bn )","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"to fund his signature campaign pledge .","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"The Democratic Party ,","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"which controls the House of Representatives ,","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"has flatly refused .","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"In a tweet on Saturday , Mr Trump said","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"negotiations between Democrats and Republicans would start immediately","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"but would not be easy","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"because both sides were `` very dug in '' .","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"In recent weeks Mr Trump has taken a hard line against thousands of migrants","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"arriving at the US southern border .","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"`` The case for national security has been greatly enhanced by what has been happening at the border and through dialogue .","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"We will build the Wall ! ''","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"he tweeted .","depth":5},{"id":31,"text":"On Friday , the Senate and House unanimously passed a bill","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"to temporarily end the shutdown ,","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"after which President Trump signed the bill into law .","depth":6},{"id":34,"text":"Following the votes in Congress","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"Mr Trump tweeted","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"that his decision was not a concession","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"but was `` taking care of the millions of people","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"who were getting badly hurt by the shutdown '' .","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"Most US media saw President Trump 's move as yielding to political pressure after the unprecedented 35-day shutdown .","depth":4},{"id":40,"text":"Speaking in the White House Rose Garden ,","depth":6},{"id":41,"text":"Mr Trump said","depth":6},{"id":42,"text":"federal workers","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"affected by the political standoff ,","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"whom he called `` incredible patriots '' ,","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"would receive full back-pay .","depth":6},{"id":46,"text":"Mr Trump also said","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"he would not yet resort to `` a very powerful alternative ''","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"- an apparent reference to declaring a national emergency .","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"Analysts say","depth":6},{"id":50,"text":"this could divert military funding towards building the border wall","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"but would provoke constitutional uproar and legal challenges .","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"On Friday , about 800,000 civil servants missed another payday amid the five-week closure of about a quarter of the federal government .","depth":2},{"id":53,"text":"Earlier , hundreds of flights were grounded or delayed at US airports","depth":6},{"id":54,"text":"because of unpaid air traffic controllers","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"calling in sick .","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"The Federal Aviation Administration","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"( FAA )","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"halted arrivals for about an hour at New York 's LaGuardia Airport .","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"Flights were also delayed at Newark Liberty International Airport and Philadelphia International Airport","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"because of staff shortages ,","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"the FAA said .","depth":7},{"id":62,"text":"Meanwhile , thousands of Internal Revenue Service","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"( IRS )","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"employees failed to show up","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"after they were ordered to return to work","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"unpaid ,","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"the Washington Post reported .","depth":6},{"id":68,"text":"The Trump administration recalled 26,000 IRS workers this week","depth":7},{"id":69,"text":"to handle the looming tax filing season .","depth":7},{"id":70,"text":"But about 14,000 of them did not come back as of Tuesday ,","depth":7},{"id":71,"text":"IRS officials told members of Congress .","depth":7},{"id":72,"text":"In a video message to agents on Friday , FBI Director Christopher Wray said :","depth":6},{"id":73,"text":"`` I 'm about as angry","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"as I 've been in a long , long time . ''","depth":7},{"id":75,"text":"Of the shutdown 's effects on his agency , he said :","depth":6},{"id":76,"text":"`` It 's mind-boggling ,","depth":7},{"id":77,"text":"it 's short-sighted ,","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"and it 's unfair . ''","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"His remarks came","depth":5},{"id":80,"text":"after an FBI report this week revealed","depth":6},{"id":81,"text":"its resources were at `` breaking point '' .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":163,"left":133,"right":162,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":133,"left":112,"right":132,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":112,"left":103,"right":111,"relation":"e